      "message": "Added comments. Generally I agree about constants, but sometimes I\u0027ll get into a mental tug-of-war over wanting to have the constants control *everything*, ie. if I have `const expectedSteps \u003d 2`, then there\u0027s a part of my brain that\u0027s going to be seriously unhappy if the script isn\u0027t generated based on that constant, to enforce its truth.",
