      "writtenOn": "2020-03-12T13:36:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Why add this extra copy?  Why not just b \u003d append(b, \u0027\\n\u0027)?  You can also query the cap() of a slice to see if it will be resized or not if that matters.\n\nIn any case, the documentation should explain \"why\"",
