      "writtenOn": "2020-03-12T19:42:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Docs for io.Writer state that the implementation must not modify the slice data, which would occur if cap(b) \u003e len(b).  It made more sense to be explicit about the copy than to do it conditionally (otherwise relying on the behavior of append).",
      "parentUuid": "1b5f9f8b_42467caa",
